(1, 1, 'Mid tone - low tone - falling tone - high tone - rising tone', 'เกา เก่า เก้า เก๊า เก๋า', 'Gao gào gâo gáo găo', 'scratch - old - nine - gout - excellent', 'The mid-tone is spoken at in the middle of your vocal range. It may fall slightly at the end. The low tone is spoken at a constant or slightly falling pitch starting lower than normal speech. The falling tone starts high and then falls to a low pitch. The high tone is spoken at the top of your vocal range, rising slightly and then falling slightly. The rising tone starts low, falls slightly and then rises to a high pitch.', 'm1_1'),
