(23, 2, 'Do you have a nickname?', 'คุณมีชื่อเล่นไหมครับ', 'Khun mii chêu-lên mái khráp?', 'you - have - nickname - or not - polite particle?', 'Thai people often have long names but the nick name is always short and is used by most people in everyday life.', 'm2_10'),
